text: Anthony Jahnke (December 5, 1879 - December 12, 1953) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1953 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Świecie
